testcase.name: LoginComponent should log out a user (login state should be cleared)
LoginComponent should not log in an invalid user
LoginComponent should update error message (for displaying login error mesage to user)
LoginComponent should log in a previously registered user (not new users)
LoginComponent should update success message (for displaying login success message to user)
PostsComponent should fetch articles for current logged in user
PostsComponent should add articles when adding a follower
PostsComponent should remove articles when removing a follower
PostsComponent should filter displayed articles by the search keyword
PostsComponent should update the search keyword
ProfileService should fetch the logged in user's profile information
